DOC.brief_summary: To examine the relation between complication in Repeated Cesarean Sections and Newborn Outcome compared to number of repeated cesarean section and reasonf or surgery and personal medical information to the mother
DOC.brief_title: Relation Between Complication in Repeated Cesarean Sections, Newborn Outcome and Surgical Characteristics and Maternal Information
